@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zfllnp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.06)) + ((v0 + 0.80 / v1 + 0.84) + (v0 + 0.62 + v1 + 0.14)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp(0.70))
    tmp = ((0.18 / v0) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.34) / 0.54))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.40)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.67)
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.48) + tmp) * wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.68)))
    v2 = (0.26 / ((v1 + 0.71 / v0 + 0.16) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
